lber elbaz  the artistic director at lanvin and one of this month   s columnists  has his own attitude about luck  while he admits to being very superstitious and thinks that luck isn   t something we can control  he believes that ultimately fate rests in our own hands     luck can bring you to the door     he says     now what do you do in the room  this is up to you     k oneill wsj com   instagram  kristina oneill 
